column2: SELECT    p.objid,p.field,p.ra,p.dec,p.insideMask,p.flags,p.probPSF,p.PSFMag_r, p.PSFMagErr_r,p.cModelMag_r,p.cModelMagErr_r,p.flags_r,p.type_r,p.PSFfwhm_r,    s.specobjid,s.z as redshift_spec, s.zErr as redshift_specErr, s.class,    s.zWarning, p1.z as redshift_phot, p1.zErr as redshift_photErr into mydb.sdss_dr1#_jul7    FROM PhotoObj AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = p.objid      JOIN Photoz AS p1 ON p1.ObjID = p.objid WHERE s.class = &&& and p.type_r = &&&
